text.tspan: If you only want to send the file to razorlab or another laser cutting company all you have to do is to delete all layers (including this one)
except "all on one layer" and "Design Template". This file is made for 5mm thick plates. Don't forget to change stroke width and color !
All other layers are guides to make it easier to change the design if you want to, presenting the hand holding the teensy.
If you do edit this design, for the other hand don't forget to remove the teensy and breakout board cutout to keep cost down
since you can fit the i2c anywhere by bending its pins.
